text: Mario Judah (Born Dec 6, 1999) is an American rapper, singer-songwriter, and record producer. Judah began to produce music at the age of 19 in 2017. He rose to fame as an internet meme with his single, "Die Very Rough" and his criticism of American rapper Playboi Carti. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:American rappers Category:American singer-songwriters Category:American record producers
